<!-- Feel the Troubled Water -->
	<thing
		id="maFtTrWt"
		name="Feel the Troubled Water"
		compset="Magic"
		isunique="yes"
		description="The diviner is able to sense unnatural disturbances to energy flows. Where a particular places has been witness to a violation of the laws of Heaven, whether by the dead returning to the world of the living, the action of demons, or the performance of a rite by the followers of Gonggong, that place is cursed forever, becoming a place of darkness and great misfortune for any who chance to pass through it. By succeeding in a Test of Earth + Divination, with an ST of 7, the diviner can tell whether a particular location is cursed. But he will not be able to say what exactly occurred to create the curse.">
		
