<!-- On the Path of the Yellow Sources -->
	<thing
		id="maPath"
		name="On the Path of the Yellow Sources"
		compset="Magic"
		isunique="yes"
		description="With this technique, a diviner can sense a person's intimate connection with death, and gain an impression of how long the person has left to live. He can tell if the person is in danger, if his life hangs by a thread, or indeed if the person is fated to lead a long and peaceful life. While he can guess at when death might come, he cannot say how. This particular rite requires the presence of the relevant person, and a successful Test of Earth + Divination against an ST of 9. The key elements of the rite take only a matter of minutes, but many diviners like to impress laymen by adorning it with a range of arcane gestures and incantations.">
		
